  • [Netflix Licensed, Enjoy Seamless Streaming] The Auking smart projector supports over 1,000,000 videos from certified apps like Netflix, allowing you to stream your favorite shows and movies seamlessly. Need more apps? Just download them online with ease, ensuring convenience without the need for external devices. Netflix projector turns your home into a full-fledged entertainment center with just one projector.
  • [Innovative Autofocus and Dual-Band WiFi Connectivity]AuKing auto-focus projector utilizes advanced high-precision sensors and displacement gyroscopes for rapid auto-focus and image correction within seconds. Enjoy sharp, clear images and effortless setup without manual adjustments, ensuring a seamless viewing experience every time.AuKing WiFi projector also features dual-band WiFi 6 technology, capable of receiving WiFi signals on two frequencies simultaneously, enhancing flexibility for faster and smoother transmission.
  • [Unique Removable and Foldable Stand]The Auking movie projector comes with an adjustable stand that allows you to easily project onto walls or ceilings, enabling you to watch movies at any angle. This means you can enjoy films comfortably whether sitting or lying down. Unlike traditional integrated stands, Outdoor projector stand is removable and foldable, making it ideal for outdoor use. Its compact design ensures easy portability without sacrificing stability. When you don’t need the stand, simply remove it for more convenience.
  • [800ANSI & 4K Support, Detail-first Visual Feast]This 4K projector features 800 ANSI lumens and supports 4K input, ensuring crystal-clear images with stunning detail. With advanced LCD Pro and color reproduction technology, AuKing video projector is at least 98% brighter and clearer than other 1080P projectors, delivering natural light and dark filtering along with sharp contrast, enhancing realism and vividness in every scene.
  • [Immersive Dolby Audio Experience & Bidirectional Bluetooth] AuKing home theater projector features Dolby-certified Hi-Fi stereo dual speakers, delivering an immersive 3D sound experience. Advanced AI sound balancing technology ensures delicate sound quality and smooth transitions. Blurtooth Projector comes with two-way Bluetooth connectivity allows you to effortlessly connect your devices to stream audio directly or use the projector as a Bluetooth speaker for your favorite music.
  • [Note]Make sure to connect 4K devices (such as a TV stick) via HDMI to play the video. Tip: Videos labelled as 4K will be displayed at the original resolution of 1080P. As mentioned in the text, "4K supported".
